@startuml
title Vault Management - Class Diagram (Current)
set namespaceSeparator none
left to right direction
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam class {
  BackgroundColor #f7e9dc
  BorderColor #d9c2a8
}
hide empty members

class "vault_management.py\n(command handlers)" as Delivery <<delivery>> {
  +init_handler(...)
  +status_handler(...)
  +rotate_handler(...)
  +rewrap_handler(...)
  +delete_key_handler(...)
  +run_maintenance_handler(...)
}

class "VaultAdminPasswordGate" as AdminGate {
  +verify_manual_access(non_interactive: bool)
}

class "VaultKeyManagementUseCase" as KeyMgmt {
  +init_keyring(...): VaultKeyManagementResult
  +status(): VaultKeyManagementStatus
  +rotate_and_rewrap(...): VaultKeyManagementResult
  +rewrap_all_dek(...): VaultKeyManagementResult
  +delete_key(...): VaultKeyManagementResult
  +finalize_inflight_bridge(...): VaultKeyManagementResult?
}

class "VaultMaintenanceUseCase" as Maintenance {
  +run_if_due(): VaultMaintenanceResult
}

class "VaultRotationPolicy" as RotationPolicy {
  +is_due(last_rotated_at, now_utc): bool
}

interface "VaultManagedKeyringStoreProtocol" as IKeyring <<protocol>> {
  +lifecycle_lock(): ContextManager[None]
  +load_keyring(): tuple[VaultMasterKey,...]
  +save_keyring(keys): None
}

interface "VaultPostVerifyProtocol" as IPostVerify <<protocol>> {
  +ensure_ready(keyring): None
}

interface "SecretVaultRepositoryPort" as IRepository <<protocol>> {
  +transaction(): ContextManager[None]
  +list_deks(): tuple[VaultDekRecord,...]
  +upsert_dek(record): None
  +set_last_rotation_result(result, reason): None
  +set_last_rotated_at(iso_utc): None
}

interface "SecretCipherPort" as ICipher <<protocol>> {
  +wrap_dek(...)
  +unwrap_dek(...)
}

class "VaultManagedEnvKeyringStore" as KeyringStore
class "VaultStartupGuardPostVerifier" as PostVerifier
class "SqliteVaultRepository" as SqliteRepo
class "FernetEnvelopeCipher" as Cipher
class "vault_startup_resource()\n(containers.py)" as Startup <<delivery>>

Delivery --> AdminGate : verifies manual access
Delivery --> KeyMgmt : manual operations
Delivery --> Maintenance : run-maintenance

Maintenance --> KeyMgmt : delegates lifecycle
Maintenance --> RotationPolicy : due-check

KeyMgmt --> IKeyring : lock/load/save keyring
KeyMgmt --> IRepository : transaction + metadata
KeyMgmt --> ICipher : unwrap/wrap DEK
KeyMgmt --> IPostVerify : post-operation verify

KeyringStore ..|> IKeyring
PostVerifier ..|> IPostVerify
SqliteRepo ..|> IRepository
Cipher ..|> ICipher

Startup --> KeyringStore : preload managed keyring
Startup --> Maintenance : optional auto-rotation
Startup --> KeyMgmt : bridge finalization path

note right of KeyMgmt
  Boundary:
  - orchestrates lifecycle protocol
  - no CLI parsing / no direct SQL
  - keeps single-key steady-state
end note

note bottom of Delivery
  CLI flags are handled here:
  --force, --dry-run, --non-interactive,
  --verify/--no-verify, --managed-env-file
end note

@enduml
